{"id":166,"ayahs":[{"number":131,"arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتْهُمُ ٱلْحَسَنَةُ قَالُوا۟ لَنَا هَٰذِهِۦ ۖ وَإِن تُصِبْهُمْ سَيِّئَةٌۭ يَطَّيَّرُوا۟ بِمُوسَىٰ وَمَن مَّعَهُۥٓ ۗ أَلَآ إِنَّمَا طَٰٓئِرُهُمْ عِندَ ٱللَّهِ وَلَٰكِنَّ أَكْثَرَهُمْ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"But whenever good fortune alighted upon them, they would say, \"This is [but] our due\"; and whenever affliction befell them, they would blame their evil fortune on Moses and those who followed him. Oh, verily, their [evil] fortune had been decreed by God-but most of them knew it not.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1085.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":78122,"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78123,"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَتْهُمُ","translation":"কাছে আসে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78124,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْحَسَنَةُ","translation":"কল্যাণ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78125,"position":4,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78126,"position":5,"arabic":"لَنَا","translation":"\"জন্যে আমাদের (অধিকার)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78127,"position":6,"arabic":"هَـٰذِهِۦ ۖ","translation":"\"এটা\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78129,"position":7,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78130,"position":8,"arabic":"تُصِبْهُمْ","translation":"পৌঁছে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78131,"position":9,"arabic":"سَيِّئَةٌۭ","translation":"কোনো অকল্যাণ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78132,"position":10,"arabic":"يَطَّيَّرُوا۟","translation":"তারা মন্দভাগ্যের দোষ চাপায়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78133,"position":11,"arabic":"بِمُوسَىٰ","translation":"উপর মূসার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78134,"position":12,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"ও (তাদের উপর) যারা (ছিলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78135,"position":13,"arabic":"مَّعَهُۥٓ ۗ","translation":"সাথে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78137,"position":14,"arabic":"أَلَآ","translation":"জেনে রাখো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78138,"position":15,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","translation":"প্রকৃতপক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78139,"position":16,"arabic":"طَـٰٓئِرُهُمْ","translation":"মন্দভাগ্য তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78140,"position":17,"arabic":"عِندَ","translation":"কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78141,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহরই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78142,"position":19,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنَّ","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78143,"position":20,"arabic":"أَكْثَرَهُمْ","translation":"অধিকাংশই তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78144,"position":21,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78145,"position":22,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"জানে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_131_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78146,"position":23,"arabic":"١٣١","translation":"(১৩১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":132,"arabic":"وَقَالُوا۟ مَهْمَا تَأْتِنَا بِهِۦ مِنْ ءَايَةٍۢ لِّتَسْحَرَنَا بِهَا فَمَا نَحْنُ لَكَ بِمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"And they said [unto Moses]: \"Whatever sign thou mayest produce before us in order to cast a spell upon us thereby, we shall not believe thee!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1086.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":78220,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَالُوا۟","translation":"এবং তারা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78221,"position":2,"arabic":"مَهْمَا","translation":"\"যা কিছুই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78222,"position":3,"arabic":"تَأْتِنَا","translation":"আমাদের কাছে আসো তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78223,"position":4,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"নিয়ে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78224,"position":5,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78225,"position":6,"arabic":"ءَايَةٍۢ","translation":"নিদর্শন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78226,"position":7,"arabic":"لِّتَسْحَرَنَا","translation":"জন্যে আমাদের যাদু করার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78227,"position":8,"arabic":"بِهَا","translation":"দিয়ে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78228,"position":9,"arabic":"فَمَا","translation":"তবুও না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78229,"position":10,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","translation":"আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78230,"position":11,"arabic":"لَكَ","translation":"উপর তোমার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78231,"position":12,"arabic":"بِمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"মু'মিন\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_132_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78232,"position":13,"arabic":"١٣٢","translation":"(১৩২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":133,"arabic":"فَأَرْسَلْنَا عَلَيْهِمُ ٱلطُّوفَانَ وَٱلْجَرَادَ وَٱلْقُمَّلَ وَٱلضَّفَادِعَ وَٱلدَّمَ ءَايَٰتٍۢ مُّفَصَّلَٰتٍۢ فَٱسْتَكْبَرُوا۟ وَكَانُوا۟ قَوْمًۭا مُّجْرِمِينَ","translation":"Thereupon We let loose upon them floods, and [plagues of] locusts, and lice, and frogs, and [water turning into] blood -distinct signs [all]: but they gloried in their arrogance, for they were people lost in sin.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1087.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":78317,"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَرْسَلْنَا","translation":"অতঃপর পাঠালাম আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78318,"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمُ","translation":"উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78319,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلطُّوفَانَ","translation":"বন্যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78320,"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْجَرَادَ","translation":"ও পঙ্গপাল","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78321,"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْقُمَّلَ","translation":"ও উকুন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78322,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلضَّفَادِعَ","translation":"ও ব্যাঙ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78323,"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱلدَّمَ","translation":"ও রক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78324,"position":8,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتٍۢ","translation":"নিদর্শনরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78325,"position":9,"arabic":"مُّفَصَّلَـٰتٍۢ","translation":"(পৃথক পৃথক ভাবেও) স্পষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78326,"position":10,"arabic":"فَٱسْتَكْبَرُوا۟","translation":"তবুও তারা অহংকার করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78327,"position":11,"arabic":"وَكَانُوا۟","translation":"এবং তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78328,"position":12,"arabic":"قَوْمًۭا","translation":"সম্প্রদায়","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78329,"position":13,"arabic":"مُّجْرِمِينَ","translation":"অপরাধী","audioUrl":"wbw/007_133_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78330,"position":14,"arabic":"١٣٣","translation":"(১৩৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":134,"arabic":"وَلَمَّا وَقَعَ عَلَيْهِمُ ٱلرِّجْزُ قَالُوا۟ يَٰمُوسَى ٱدْعُ لَنَا رَبَّكَ بِمَا عَهِدَ عِندَكَ ۖ لَئِن كَشَفْتَ عَنَّا ٱلرِّجْزَ لَنُؤْمِنَنَّ لَكَ وَلَنُرْسِلَنَّ مَعَكَ بَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ","translation":"And whenever a plague struck them, they would cry: \"O Moses, pray for us to thy Sustainer on the strength of the covenant [of prophethood] which He has made with thee! If thou remove this plague from us, we will truly believe in thee. and will let the children of Israel go with thee!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1088.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":78394,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَمَّا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78395,"position":2,"arabic":"وَقَعَ","translation":"সংঘটিত হতো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78396,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمُ","translation":"উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78397,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلرِّجْزُ","translation":"কোনো শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78398,"position":5,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলতো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78399,"position":6,"arabic":"يَـٰمُوسَى","translation":"\"হে মূসা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78400,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱدْعُ","translation":"তুমি দোয়া করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78401,"position":8,"arabic":"لَنَا","translation":"জন্যে আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78402,"position":9,"arabic":"رَبَّكَ","translation":"তোমার রবের কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78403,"position":10,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":78404,"position":11,"arabic":"عَهِدَ","translation":"অঙ্গীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_134_011.mp3","charT